<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c1">"الصحيحة"</span> <span class="c2">(٤/ ٦٠٥)</span>.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c4">[[١٤٣٩]</span> باب من فضائل طلحة بن عبيد الله الأنصاري]<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
